snippet.title: Nick Jr Party Adventure | Announce Trailer | UK | PEGI
snippet.description:
Get ready to party with your favourite Nick Jr.’ characters as they prepare to celebrate the Friendship Fiesta in Nick Jr. Party Adventure, coming to PC, Xbox, Playstation and Nintendo Switch this October! 

Team up with characters from 6 beloved Nick Jr. shows - PAW Patrol®, Dora, Blue's Clues & You!, Blaze and the Monster Machines, Bubble Guppies, and Santiago of the Seas for an exciting journey across the vibrant Nick Jr. world. Solve interactive puzzles, discover hidden collectibles, and join family and friends in up to 2-player local co-op!  🎉
